data.description: You don't want to miss out on this recently upgraded 4 bedroom 2 bath room waterfront home with 1 car garage.  New roof 2017, New central AC and Upgraded Kitchen & Bathrooms, Tile throughout, Plus a HUGE Patio with a Very Private Large Fenced Yard with Shed that back up to a Preserve with a Beautiful Water view. Great floor plan gives this home a Big Open Appearance inside and is located in an Excellent Location only- 5 Miles from Jensen Beach and Martin County and is Very close to Treasure Coast Square Mall, All Restaurants, Walmart, Lowe's, BJS & Sams Club. SELLERS VERY MOTIVATED
